name: Milano Ultrasonic Usb Diffuser With 10 Aroma Oils 130Ml
description:
MILANO ULTRASONIC USB DIFFUSER WITH 10 AROMA OILS 130ML


Light-weight and simple to use just add water a few drops of your favourite scent and just plug it into any USB and with the press of a button a fine cooling mist is generated by ultrasonic technology to add moisture into the surrounding environment.

Experience a soothing serene aromatherapy oasis with the USB Diffuser with 10 Aroma Oils designed by Milano Decor.

FEATURES

Available Colours: Dark Wood, Light Wood

Brand: Milano

Create a soothing serene aromatherapy oasis

Fine cooling mist that is generated by ultrasonic technology

Comes with 10 aroma oils: Orange Lavender Tea Tree Peppermint Eucalyptus

Lemongrass Jasmine Rose Bergamot Sandalwood

Ultra-lightweight and portable

USB plug-in making it great for travel or home

130ml tank capacity

Operates for up to 3 hours continuous use

Auto safety shut off function when water level run low

SPECIFICATIONS

Water Capacity: 130ml

Product Weight: 150 grams

USB Dimensions: 9.7cm x 9.7cm x 9.7cm

Mist Output: 25ml/hour

Working Time: 3 Hours

Mode: Continuous

Voltage: DC5 Volts

PACKAGE CONTENTS

1 x Diffuser

10 x 10ml aroma oils

1 x USB Adapter

1 x Instruction Manual (English)
